Im in a very great mood today! BWEEEE! Today is mine and Louis' 1 month anniversary, YEY! Also today is my last day here at owens. W007!!! That means I get to sleep now PRAISE BE TO J33bu5! N E ways 2 nite we're going out to dinner, then we're going back to his place to watch a movie....hopefully I'll talk him into doing a little DDR somewhere in between. I have no klew where we're going to eat, and he won't tell me. I hate it when they do that *anime sweatdrop*

man.....i need to lay off the sugar......*strips nekkid and frollics*BWEEEEEEEE!!

Wow I'm in such a great mood. I've spent pretty much every day for the past 2 weeks with my boyfriend. God, he's gorgeous. Anyways, it's been so awesome. I love his parents; they're so cute and cynical. ^_^  It was such a great night last night. We drove to downtown Perrysburg (wich consists of like 10 shops and a dog) and walked to the Perry statue. ( i know its starting to sound like the SM*RFING SMURFS......sonnofasmurf). So we get to the statue and sit on a bench and he held me in his arms to keep me warm. It was sooo sweet. So thats whats going on with me. dooobeeedooo

Well, at first easter seemed that it was going to be shitty. My parents decided that we weren't going to go anywhere for easter, and we weren't having easter dinner. :(  But then Louis called. ^_^    (for those of you who don't know Louis is my new boi toy). He invited me over to have easter dinner with him and his family. It was so much fun. Then we went to his German teacher's house (he's house sitting). 
This house has 4 floors, and 4 bedrooms....needless to say, we had fun ^_~*    That poor leather couch never saw it cumming.....oops, i mean coming. *teehee*

  Well, i should probably get back to scooping ice cream, and making cakes.

Wow....last night was quite interresting. First off I broke things off with Kolt(Halleluja). That just went to hell in a handbasket. If you want to know the details all of you have my #. N e ways. I'm so happy that I broke things off with that sonnofabitch. He was just using me for money, bastard. But, I'm much happier now. ^_^

I find it so odd that just when you think that nothing could possibly go wrong*BAM*reality hits you square in the nuts and spits in your face! One more reason that optomism will never win. Y'know, more and more people are telling me that,"since you came you you're more of a bitch." No, along with hiding my sexuality I also hid the fact that I'm sick and f*cking tired of being walked all over. So, now that I'm completelely being myself people are realizing that they didn't really know me at all....and others wish that they didn't. And to the annonymous writer...you're right. I'm pathetic, I have no life, no hope, and no heart. I'm a cold hearted bitch that desrves to burn in hell. So, if anyone wants to take me up on that offer i've got a shotgun and a bullet with my name on it, KNOCK YOURSELF OUT! I just don't care anymore.

Yey, Tony got a boyfriend!!! ^_^    Let's see....His name is Kolt, he's about 6'1", he's 16, and gorgeous ^#^   Well, what happened was I met him and got a crush on him....well, the next week (yesterday to be specific) we were at RAY(its a gay youth group i go to) and he started coming on to me  0.o  So I was like, 'woah'. Well after the meeting we all went to this coffee house, and he asked me out ^_^   I said yes....then when he got ready to leave I went outside with him, he grabbed me by my shirt, pulled me close and kissed me ^#^  WOW. So, Tony is on cloud 9 right now. Here's a piccyture of him ^_^ BWEEE

So, my so called "friend" Julie McDonald.....now my favorite self-richeous, anal retentive ass licking bitch......decided to start telling people that i came out. Even though she never asked me, and she doesn't even know for sure. Well now the bitch is gonna pay! I have so much blackmail on her that if i let it all out she'd have to move out of this state. I hate to have to do that but if she doesn't drop this shit i'm gonna make sure that she can't show her face in public! I mean i ALWAYS have to listen to her bitch about her boyfriend and her parents, but the first thing she does when she hears a rumor about me is spread it?! FUCK HER!!!! I'm going to tell her off so badly tomorrow that it would make a sailor blush!

I AM SO SICK AND TIRED OF THIS SHIT!!! This is the second time I've gotten used this month! Ok so this is how last night went...get home and i have to write this damned outline, it took all of 15 minutes. Then I eat dinner, and have to do the dishes, they took a half an hour. After the dishes I had to go upstairs into our new second floor and help with the remodeling. I was up there for about 2 hrs. I come downstairs to take a shower and see that i missed a call. So i call the person back, it turns out to be this 15 year old guy that i've been helping on this message board. So, we get to talking and he asks me if I'm,"interrested?"
WTF?! So I ask him why he's interrested in me and he says that he isn't and that I'm assuming things! WHAT THE FLYING FUCK?! So, then while i'm still talking to the fucker my mom comes in my room and says that we need to have a family meeting....yeah, what i heard was,"hey lets start another holocaust!" So, i sit in the living room and all hell breaks loose! Dad starts yelling that we don't do jack shit around the house, then ashley TELLS HIM OFF!(mad props to her, she's got some balls!) HE GOT PISSED! He slams down his beer on the GLASS COASTER and breaks the fucker to kingdom come. Thats when my mom gets upset. So now everyone is yelling and i'm sitting there in the fetal position rocking back and forth trying not to completely loose it. That arguement took 3 FUCKING HOURS!!! I'm at 99.9% capasity of other peoples bull shit and i am [----] <---that close to losing it!

Well, today has really sucked! FIRST I had to get up at 6 o'fucking clock in the morning so that I could go to this damned orchestra competition. THEN I get home and find out that I'm getting a C+ in my English class (Mr. Ricard can kiss my ass). Now I'm getting ready to go to work....oh so much fun, but that's not the best of it....OH NO, FAR FROM IT! The orchestra is having a party tonight for getting a 1 at competition today, but here's the catch....IT'S AT MY BOSSES HOUSE!!!! THAT'S RIGHT. THE SONOFABITCH OWNS EVERYTHING EVEN THE ORCHESTRA!!! So, not only am I missing a party, I'm stuck working for the ass that's having the party. YES I'M A BITCH TODAY AND I DONT GIVE A FLYING FUCK!!!! I have MANY MANY other things that I'm pissed at right now but I cant post them in my live journal because it could OFFEND people. FUCK THAT!
kino wa omoshirokatta deshita yo!!! thats all i got to say about that.

I had originally logged on to rant, but then I began to read Brock's post and remembered what a great guy he is and how lucky I am to be his friend. He really is a nice guy, he just doesn't give himself enough credit. Honestly, if he didn't try so hard and was just himself he might be more self-confident. He has a lot to be proud of, I've only known him for about a semester and I've already learned that he's great at Japanese, he's definitesy a great people person, and everyone that I talk to thinks that he's a really great guy....I just wish that he could see that. 
     He reminds me a lot of my old best friend, it feels like there's something there that he won't ("can't") tell anyone. I've taken psychology and I think that I know enough about people to deduce that people who seem to be happy all the time are the people that are really sad down inside. And, though, Brock is always happy in class and around me I can tell that there's something there, something deep. Well, that's just my opinion anyways. If there IS something there I hope that someday he could trust me enough to tell me ^_^ because it was hiding things that slowly ate away one of the best friendships that I ever had.
     Also, I would like to get to know Adam and Nathan better (they're in my Jap. class) they seem to be friendly and generally great guys. Well, I'm off to play GO. SAYONARA! ^_~*

The other day after work i went to Meijer with some co-workers. It was definitely omoshirokata!(interesting) First of all Ashley(one co-worker) is on crutches so when we got there we decided for her to use one of those electric carts 0.o that was something else!! Then we were wandering around the store and I saw something that I just HAD to get....A THONG! That's right Tony bought a THONG. And might I add they aren't that uncomfortable. It took me a while to get used to it. Omoshirokatta deshita. I think I got it mostly just to say that I had one. Well, I should probably go and make a birthday card for nathan-kun. Ano, ja mata desho.

I sat in on Japanese 1 this past weekend, it was a BLAST! I was there with Ben-san and Neko-chan (two of my best buddies)^#^ .Anyways, I met this new guy, I think he's about 19 or something, doesn't matter, anyways it seems that he's VERY into Japanese just like I am. Thats kewl. I gave him my phone number and the Jap. club website in case he wanted to practice his new mad Japanese skills. I know it's really hard to learn how to speak Japanese when the only two times you get a chance are on the weekends in class, and when you're doing dishes speaking Japanese to yourself(hoping that no one thinks you're crazy) ^#^. Although, I've been told that you're only crazy if you answer yourself back (which I do quite frequently) ^_~*
Well, I gtg so shout out to all my homies! (yeah i know pretty lame coming from a white boy)Thanks to all of you that reply to my bitchy posts, you make me feel a lot better ^_^
